data.title: Westminster Christian School Athletics Hall of Fame A Private preK
data.text:
The Westminster Athletic Hall of Fame

The Westminster Athletic Hall of Fame honors the achievements of former Warrior athletes who have made a positive impact on the school's athletic program through their athletic abilities and Christian witness.

Westminster is currently accepting nominations for both athletes and coaches to the Hall of Fame. For athletes, nominees must have graduated from Westminster at least three years prior and demonstrated a clear Christian testimony while at Westminster Christian. Coaches need to have served at least 10 years as a Varsity Head Coach at Westminster and demonstrated exemplary Christian leadership and mentorship.

Nominations are screened by the Hall of Fame Committee, who then create a final ballot that is voted on by all members of the Westminster Hall of Fame.
